Title: Fermi-Bose duality via extra dimension

Authors: A.A.Slavnov

Comments: 7 pages, LATEX

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B388 (1996) 147-153

Representation of a $D$-dimensional fermion determinant as a path integral ofexponent of a $(D+1)$-dimensional Hermitean bosonic action is constructed.